{"tid":937151,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"高手請入，車房換完士撻ABS燈就著左","createTime":"2018-12-11T10:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T04:46:57.000Z","uid":37603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ceca55b857119a8a4913f9d99044bfda38b10524","tid":937151,"uid":37603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"朝早撻唔著架車，搵左附近車房搞，開頭懷疑係電池冇電，最後話係士撻要換，換完打黎同我講ABS燈著左，Check返係要換ABS泵，2手都要跌幾千，我心諗有冇咁唔好彩...<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有經驗話我知有冇可能換士撻會整壞個ABS泵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBMW 2009 E60"},{"pid":"8f4ab04889ff73edc8f0afd3c12bd06ccf254d9f","tid":937151,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"有竟棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf412c18c5d2b57065052c60413c644a2e97cf7b","tid":937151,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"附近車房係咪相熟先<br />\n唔熟你自己就諗諗喇, 不過而家你架車個ABS泵應該真係壞既"},{"pid":"82dc8294e4517782dd3caf5207b9ea9d72bca0bf","tid":937151,"uid":37603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf412c18c5d2b57065052c60413c644a2e97cf7b","tid":937151,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"附近車房係咪相熟先<br />\n唔熟你自己就諗諗喇, 不過而家你架車個ABS泵應該真係壞既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"之前搵過幾次，係個老阿叔自己做，不過主要係搞我第二架車(Honda Stream)，都傾得下計，Feel到佢唔太熟歐洲車，佢最後都係幫我拎去第間佢熟既車房搞，中間唔知發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n而家我問左另一間專搞歐洲車既車房，佢地話亂咁試個士撻都有可能燒到個ABS泵。我當日就係見條友係度狂按個Start Engine掣，有d懷疑係咪個時做成，但又冇証據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25931af8dc